cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper presents a method for 3D object detection using multi-view inputs, which involves computer vision (CV) and robotics (RO) techniques. The method also involves feature fusion, which is a common topic in machine learning (LG), artificial intelligence (AI), and natural language processing (CL). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.CL.
